00328 inline void Eval_Grad_VDF_Face::flux_fa7_elem(const DoubleTab& inco, int elem,
00329                                               int fac1, int, DoubleVect& flux) const
00330 {
00331   for (int k=0; k<flux.size(); k++)
00332     flux(k) = inco(elem,k)*surface(fac1);
00333 }

00335 ////!< flux_fa7_sortie_libre 
00336 //
00337 
00338 inline void Eval_Grad_VDF_Face::flux_fa7_sortie_libre(const DoubleTab& , int face,
00339                                                       const Neumann_sortie_libre& la_cl,
00340                                                       int num1,DoubleVect& flux) const
00341 {
